* Richardson, Peter, &quot;Savage Journey: Hunter S. Thompson and the Weird Road to Gonzo&quot; (). Berkeley: University of California Press, 2022. .
* Wills, David S., &quot;High White Notes: The Rise and Fall of Gonzo Journalism&quot; (). Edinburgh: Beatdom Books, 2022. .

