* Lillian Rosanoff Lieber (1886-1986), Russian-American mathematician and author
* Audre Lorde (1934–1992), poet
* Marguerite Merington (1857–1951), author
* Robert Motherwell, artist
* Carrie Moyer, artist
* Colum McCann, Irish novelist
